Text-based FilterJSON-based filter <pre><code>citydb export citygml --filter="name = 'Forest tree 3'" -o filtered_tree.gml
</code></pre> <pre><code>{
  "op": "=",
  "args": [
    { "property": "name" },
    "Forest tree 3"
  ]
}
</code></pre>

Text-based filterJSON-based filter LinuxWindows <pre><code>citydb export citygml \
      --filter="name = 'Forest tree 3' AND height &gt; '1'" \
      -o filtered_tree.gml
</code></pre> <pre><code>citydb export citygml ^
      --filter="name = 'Forest tree 3' AND height &gt; '1'" ^
      -o filtered_tree.gml
</code></pre> <pre><code>{
  "op": "AND",
  "args": [
    {
      "op": "=",
      "args": [
        { "property": "name" },
        "Forest tree 3"
      ]
    },
    {
      "op": "&gt;",
      "args": [
        { "property": "height" },
        "1"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
</code></pre>
